name: Jordan Vogt-Roberts
bio: From the ashes a fire shall be woken, A light from the shadows shall spring; Renewed shall be blade that was broken. I direct movies. King Kong’s dad.

social_posts.post_text: Happy Fathers Day. I miss you every day. Hope I’m making you proud. I keep you alive in my every day and hope you may live on through the stories I tell and incalculable impact you had on letting me chase my wild dreams. Love you, daddy.
Had a day to myself with the Yokohama Gundam. Thanks to the team at at Bandai Namco Film Works for making this happen. 📸 @chojnowski
Fushimi Inari-Taisha aka the Star Fox shrine.

Today was the last day in my life that I lived without piloting a Mech.

More details soon…
Always love seeing the incredible artist and human that is @kaidayuji.

It was an honor to speak to the next generation of Japanese filmmakers and manga artists today about how my creative process goes from inception to storyboards, to previs, to final product. Thanks to TOHO and SHUEISHA for allowing arranging all of this and congratulations to all the finalists in the World Maker competition. It was my absolute pleasure to meet everyone and can’t wait to see what you do next!

@detroitlionsnfl ALL DAY.

@kylemccarthy and @bradgalli coming through heavy.
